  <section id="about" class="my-5">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="card col-md-7 ">
          <img src="/static/image/img/img-1.png" class="img-fluid py-2" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-5 mt-md-5 mt-1">
          <h2>We take pride in sourcing the freshest and highest quality ingredients.</h2>
          <p>Our secret ingredients for every dish are the perfect blend of nutrition, health, and a generous sprinkle of love. We believe that food is not just sustenance, but a way to nourish both body and soul. Experience the wholesome goodness and passion we put into every meal we deliver.</p>
