          <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active"
            aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
          <button type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-bs-slide-to="1"
            aria-label="Slide 2"></button>

        </div>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item text-center active">
            <img style="width:150px;height:auto;border-radius:50%" src="/static/image/review/review-1.jpg" alt="...">
            <div class="my-4">
              <h4 class="">John K Leone</h4>
              <p class="text-light">"I have been ordering from this online food delivery site for months now, and I must say, they never disappoint. The food always arrives fresh, hot, and packed with flavor. It's like having a gourmet restaurant experience right at my doorstep!.".</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item text-center ">
            <img style="width:150px;height:auto; border-radius:50%" src="/static/image/review/review-2.jpg" alt="...">
            <div class="my-4">
              <h4 class="">Nancy Whiller</h4>
              <p class="text-light">"I highly recommend this online food delivery site! Their diverse menu options cater to all my dietary preferences, and the quality of the ingredients truly shines through in every bite. Plus, their prompt and efficient delivery service makes it incredibly convenient. It's my go-to choice for delicious meals without the hassle of cooking."</p>
            </div>
          </div>


